ADMIRALTY TOTAL TIDES 2020 ADVISORY.
1. BE ADVISED THAT ADMIRALTY TOTAL TIDES (ATT) DISCS
   DISTRIBUTED IN LATE 2019 (EDITION 21) MAY NOT
   INSTALL CORRECTLY. NGA RECOMMENDS INSTALLING
   EDITION 21 OVER A PREVIOUS VERSION OF ATT.
   OTHERWISE, IT MAY NOT INSTALL CORRECTLY.
2. ATT HAS BEEN CORRECTED AND EDITION 22 WILL BE
   DISTRIBUTED BY DLA AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.
3. ATT, EDITION 20, WILL REMAIN VALID UNTIL 31 MAR 20.
4. CANCEL THIS MSG 01 APR 20.
